description: The Fall Election's final eight prepare for battle, and Soma is up in the first round! What bento will he create to combat the molecular gastronomy genius, Alice Nakiri?

input: That Which is Placed Within the Box
Which is Placed Within the Box

title: That Which is Placed Within the Box

description: Soma's reckless streak flared up again and it's landed him and Megumi in hot water. Their opponent is no student this time, but a magician!

input: The Magician That Came from the East
Magician That Came from the East

title: The Magician That Came from the East

description: It's Megumi's chance to show off her skills. As Soma takes a supporting role, this time it's her cooking that will have to save the day!

input: The Memory of a Single Dish

title: The Memory of a Single Dish

description: Soma's dish is literally deflating! It will take every ounce of his focus to get back on track, but it might be too late.
title: Metamorphose

description: The training camp lives up to its brutal reputation as the exhausted students are given two choices at the end of day three!
title: Eggs Before the Dawn

description: Soma and his team work on a tasty, original and portable dish to combat the Mozuya invasion. They'll have to make their mark on the Sumire shopping district or watch it fall.
title: The Fried Chicken of Youth

description: The lists for the Fall Selection are out! When the topic is announced, Soma seeks out a former colleague of his father's and finds more than he bargained for.
title: The Chosen One

description: Soma has his first showdown with his dad in months. With Isshiki, Megumi, and Fumio judging this morning match, will this finally be Soma's first victory?

input: The Cook Who Traveled Thousands of Miles
Cook Who Traveled Thousands of Miles

title: The Cook Who Traveled Thousands of Miles

description: Over the break, Yukihira challenges a popular fried chicken shop to save his old shopping district. He's found a taste tester, but who can he call to help develop the recipe?
title: Sensual Fried Chicken

description: There's no summer break for the Fall Selection participants! Soma and the others work to enhance their dishes over the six weeks before they head into the prelims.

input: Dragon Lies Prone then Ascends to the Sky
Lies Prone then Ascends to the Sky
Prone then Ascends to the Sky

title: Dragon Lies Prone then Ascends to the Sky

description: As the members of Polar Star Dormitory finally make it home, they're treated to a meal from a surprise guest, whose fame rattles even Soma.
title: The Man Called "Carnage"

description: The Fall Selection preliminaries are underway! Megumi shocks everyone with a tricky ingredient, and the election hall is assaulted by "cursed" curry!

input: That Which is Known yet Unknown

title: That Which is Known yet Unknown

description: The prelims continue! Hoshino's curry is judged, and the Aldini brothers face off. In the wake of Alice Nakiri's dish, the judges make the mistake of almost forgetting Megumi.
title: That Which Transcends the Norm

description: With the finalists from Group B solidified, Group A is reeling as a judge continues to give zero points. Ryo Kurokiba, Alice's aide, presents a dish that surprises everyone.
title: The Unfolding Individual Competition

description: Tensions mount as Soma faces off against Akira Hayama and the finalists are chosen!
title: The Warriors' Banquet

description: With resolve and her newfound ability to keep a cool head, Megumi prepares to face Ryo in the next battle: ramen. These opposite personalities clash through their dishes!
title: Interplay of Light & Shadow

description: Subaru Mimasaka has a habit of stalking people to get in their heads, challenging them and then taking their prized tools. Will Takumi's mezzaluna be next?
title: The Pursuer

description: Soma's semi-final match against Mimasaka begins. With not only his tools, but also his future as a chef at risk, Soma prepares to fight Mimasaka's version of him.

input: The Secret of the First Bite

title: The Secret of the First Bite

description: The battle between Soma and Mimasaka begins! Immediately, Mimasaka's mimicry of Soma's dish comes into play. Can Soma beat this detail oriented "mirror" chef?
title: Morning Shall Come Again

description: Slice, stir, and serve! Your mouth might just water at this trailer for the newest show joining our Saturday night lineup. Food Wars premieres Saturday night at 1a!
title: Food Wars Trailer

description: Soma spends his days battling his father to see who is the best chef at his family restaurant. Things get complicated when a developer tries to muscle in on their land.
title: The Vast Wasteland

description: Soma goes up against a difficult foe, Erina Nakiri, owner of the "God's Tongue": her palate can literally make or break your career! Can a lowly diner chef pass her test?
title: God Tongue

description: Soma causes quite a stir at the opening ceremony, declaring his intentions to be #1. His first big obstacle: a world renowned French chef and an overly nervous teammate!
title: That Chef Doesn't Smile

description: Soma arrives at Polar Star Dormitory with high expectations, but its shabby exterior houses talented chefs, an incredible kitchen and an unexpected challenge!
title: Sacred Mother of Kyokusei

description: Another challenge is underway! Though, it's not official, and Soma soon discovers that an official challenge is something entirely different - it's a Food War.

input: The Ice Queen and the Spring Storm
Ice Queen and the Spring Storm

title: The Ice Queen and the Spring Storm

description: Soma is drawn to the Rice Bowl Research Society, only to find that it's being threatened by Erina's lackey, Ikumi Mito, nicknamed the Meat Master.
title: The Meat Aggressor

description: The Food War between Ikumi Mito and Yukihira Soma has begun! Soma will have to truly transform his cheap ingredients to combat the Meat Master's expensive beef.

input: The Silent Bowl, the Eloquent Bowl

title: The Silent Bowl, the Eloquent Bowl

description: A brutal training camp is underway. Those in Polar Star Dorm are determined to survive, but Soma may have met his match - another professional!

input: A Concerto of Concept and Creation

title: A Concerto of Concept and Creation

description: Under the alumnus Shinomiya, Soma and Megumi are given a complex "recette"  that they must follow to the letter. But Shinomiya is a cruel judge, and more severe than expected.
title: The Supreme Recette

description: Soma's fired up by Takumi Aldini's challenge and skills. With only the immediate vicinity as their pantry, Soma finds the perfect ingredient to set his dish apart.

input: The Breading that Showcases the Mountains

title: The Breading that Showcases the Mountains

description: The Totsuki students are sent off for practical experience, and Soma lands in a (very) busy family restaurant with Erina's secretary Arata! Can these two even work together?!
title: The Stagiarie

description: In the last act of the competition, Soma's creation falls short. However, his dish has a secret twist, but is it enough to win against Hayama and Ryo's masterpieces?
title: A New Jewel

description: The arena is filled with scarcely contained, feral tension as Akira Hayama and Ryo Kurokiba face off in the last round of the semi-finals.
title: Beasts That Devour Each Other

description: Soma finds himself in a strange place as the finals approach. Testing out recipes might be the last thing he has to worry about compared to the knowledge he lacks.

input: The Battle That Follows the Seasons

title: The Battle That Follows the Seasons

description: The finals are on! With an unprecedented three-way battle ahead, Soma seems like the underdog compared to Hayama and Kurokiba. Can he even finish in time?
title: The Sword That Announces Fall
